    • Appointment

      public Appointment(Double UID, Double CID, Date Edate, Date Sdate, Double ID, String title, String Description, String location, Double contact, String type, Time Stime, Time Etime)
      Parameters:
      UID - The ID for the user that created this appointment
      CID - The ID for the customer that is associated with this appointment.
      Edate - Data for the end of the appointment.
      Sdate - Data for the start of the appointment.
      ID - The ID of the contact that is associated with this appointment.
      title - The title of the appointment
      Description - A description of the appointment's purpose.
      location - The location of the appointment
      contact - The ID of the contact that is associated with this appointment.
      type - A description of what type of appointment this is.
      Stime - The start time of the appointment
      Etime - The end time of the appointment
